{"prompt": "Generate a website for a cybersecurity firm. The website should be sophisticated and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SecureSphere Cyber</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #0a192f;\n            color: #ccd6f6;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #0a192f, #112240);\n            color: #ccd6f6;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #64ffda 3px solid;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            color: #64ffda;\n        }\n        #main-content {\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        #main-content h2 {\n            color: #64ffda;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        #main-content p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto 30px auto;\n        }\n        .services {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        .service-item {\n            background: #112240;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin: 10px;\n            width: 30%;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.5);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n        }\n        .service-item h3 {\n            color: #64ffda;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .service-item p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background: #112240;\n            color: #ccd6f6;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            border-top: #64ffda 1px solid;\n        }\n        footer a {\n            color: #64ffda;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .service-item {\n                width: 80%;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>SecureSphere Cyber</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n    <div id=\"main-content\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Your Digital Fortress in a Complex World</h2>\n        <p>At SecureSphere Cyber, we provide comprehensive cybersecurity solutions tailored to protect your business from evolving threats. Our expert team leverages cutting-edge technology and industry best practices to ensure your data, systems, and reputation remain secure.</p>\n        \n        <h3>Our Services</h3>\n        <div class=\"services\">\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Threat Detection & Response</h3>\n                <p>Proactive monitoring and rapid incident response to neutralize threats before they impact your operations.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Vulnerability Management</h3>\n                <p>Identifying and mitigating weaknesses in your systems through regular assessments and penetration testing.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Security Consulting</h3>\n                <p>Strategic guidance and policy development to build a robust security posture for your organization.</p>\n      